    <categories>
        <category>Utility</category>
        <category>Office</category>
    </categories>
    <launchable type="desktop-id">org.flozz.calcleaner.desktop</launchable>
    <provides>
        <binary>calcleaner</binary>
    </provides>

    <description>
        <p>
            CalCleaner is a simple utility to purge old events from CalDAV calendars.
        </p>
        <p>
            Connect one or multiple CalDAV accounts (Nextcloud, Google Calendar, iCloud,...),
            select which calendars to clean, define the max age of events you want
            to keep and hit the "Clean Now!" button to let CalCleaner purge old
            events from your calendars. 🗓️🧹️
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="hr">
            Čistač kalendara (CalCleaner) je jednostavan alat za brisanje starih događaja iz CalDAV kalendara.
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="hr">
            Poveži se s jednim ili više CalDAV računa (Nextcloud, Google Calendar, iCloud, …), odaberi kalendare za čišćenje, odredi željenu maksimalnu starost događaja koje želiš zadržati i pritisnuti gumb „Očisti sada!” kako bi aplikacija „Čistač kalendara” izbrisala stare događaje iz tvojih kalendara. 🗓️🧹️
        </p>
    </description>

